price: (N̄ǹkan tí ẹ̀ ń jọ́sìn fún) lẹ́yìn Allāhu, ṣé wọ́n lè ràn yín lọ́wọ́ tàbí ṣé wọ́n lè ran ara wọn lọ́wọ́?
arabic: مِن دُونِ ٱللَّهِ هَلۡ يَنصُرُونَكُمۡ أَوۡ يَنتَصِرُونَ

version.title: Yoruba translation
version.description: Translation of the Quran meanings into Yoruba by Abu Rahima Mikhail Aikweiny, printed in 1432 H.

meta.transliteration: min dūni al-lahi hal yanṣurūnakum aw yantaṣirūna
